{"tid":1462843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"預左比人屌，但都要埋黎睇睇","createTime":"2019-08-13T11:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T11:29:56.000Z","uid":281477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f01551f120fea0a7a33dcbdf94009b060451c353","tid":1462843,"uid":281477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:25:27.000Z","msg":"其實真係好撚怪，噚日吹風吹撚到甘行，機場一啲事都無，甘大家嘅界線就會低咗！<br />\n<br />\n我最撚驚係一陣狗狗因為我地戒心一低，就尻衝入機場，甘就會出狗狗屠城記！<br />\n<br />\n學下禮義廉，人無恥便無敵。每日搞機場，搞到停機就閃人。重點唔係死守（死守亦冇意義），而係不合作令到旅客不便同損失，迫政府正視問題。一黎目的達到，二黎安全。"},{"pid":"b2fdf3cba6cf972b7e7e4fd441db056b53795af2","tid":1462843,"uid":281477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3e6066bdd25037b991f830186052e490da7214","tid":1462843,"uid":281477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:25:54.000Z","msg":"尻推幾下"},{"pid":"d6ed27735504f38d6bebab5bb6fdcea70bd27541","tid":1462843,"uid":281477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caddfc3d251abbfcf6b12dcac1ba71daae5f382a","tid":1462843,"uid":281477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:29:41.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"0cbfe68623bb89aa2484dd3032d688cc75319fa4","tid":1462843,"uid":281477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:29:56.000Z","msg":"推"}]}